There are no new features for this release.

None.

This document includes the new features, enhancements, and fixed issues for release 1.2.1 of Hazelcast Hibernate 5.

# New Features

There are no new features for this release.

# Enhancements

- Cluster time should be used instead of system time. [[#28]](https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast-hibernate5/pull/28)
- Hazelcast instance factory should be allowed to be changed. [[#25]](https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast-hibernate5/pull/25)

# Fixes

There are no fixes for this release.

# Known Issues

None.

body:
This document includes the new features, enhancements, and fixed issues for Hazelcast Hibernate 5 release.

# Enhancements
- Hibernate 5.2.5 compatibility
- hazelcast-client dependency becomes optional

# Fixes
- Fix invalid OSGI Export-Package clause in hazelcast-hibernate52

# Known Issues

None.

# Fixes
- `hazelcast-hibernate52` 1.1 not compatible with Hibernate 5.2.3 [[#9]](https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast-hibernate5/issues/9)

This document includes the new features, enhancements, and fixed issues for Hazelcast Hibernate-5, 1.1 release.

# New Features

There are no new features for this release.

# Enhancements
- Support for Hibernate 5.2.x added. [[#5]](https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast-hibernate5/pull/5)

# Fixes
- `NullPointerException` thrown by `ExpiryMarker#isReplaceableBy` fixed. [[#8]](https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast-hibernate5/pull/8)
- Error on build caused by JavaDoc DocLint. [[#6]](https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast-hibernate5/pull/6)

# Known Issues

None.
